fifteen, subject in the inner
voice.

00:27:42.777 --> 00:27:46.848
&gt;
 

00:27:46.848 --> 00:27:49.266
Here's our invertible
counterpoint,

00:27:49.266 --> 00:27:51.470
&gt;
 

00:27:51.470 --> 00:28:00.210
switch, &lt;&lt;music
playing&gt;&gt;

