00:28:40.740 --> 00:28:42.608
&gt;.
 

00:28:42.608 --> 00:28:42.730
Okay.
 

00:28:42.730 --> 00:28:43.460
&gt;
 

00:28:43.460 --> 00:28:45.808
And then what they do is go off
