00:32:41.759 --> 00:32:45.690
 
 

00:32:45.690 --> 00:32:46.356
Okay.
 

00:32:46.356 --> 00:32:50.759
Let me--somebody different
here.

00:32:50.759 --> 00:32:52.700
Robert, I haven't called on you
